:date 2014-05-25
:by Thomas
:title And yet more optimal with mpg123 1.20.0!
.<p>Get the fresh mpg123 1.20.0:</p>
.<ul>
.<li>Added NEON optimized decoder for AArch64 (ARM 64bit environment)</li>
.<ul>
.  <li>enabled for --with-cpu=neon64 (NEON only) or --with-cpu=aarch64 (runtime switch between neon and generic_fpu, like arm_fpu) configuration</li>
