:title Fixing your world with mpg123-1.12.2
.<p>The fresh maintenance release mainly fixes <a href="/bugs/2996045">bug 2996045</a>, invalid memory access prompted by addresses in the upper half of the address space. I introduced that one with a bad alignment algorithm, sorry.<p>
